title: Did J. Cole kick Kanye while he's down????
itunes:title: Did J. Cole kick Kanye while he's down????
description:
12/02- J. Cole blessed the hip hop world with a new track "False Prophets" and it seems he's taking shots at Kanye West and Wale. Envy, Angela and Charlamagne break down the lyrics and give their thoughts. The Donkey of the Day goes to a country star who took matters in his own hands. Shia Labeouf sent Charlamagne some heat as he disses Drake, Lil Yachty and more.
